type: Tutorial Step - Are We Ready Yet?

definition.text: Resistances and Supports Multi-Period-Daily to the left is the last of the processes to finish.

paragraphs.text: If this process is at 100%, then we are ready to go.

Either way, nothing catastrophic happens if you attempt to run a Live Trading Session when the required indicators are not up to date. There would be an error, and you'd be notified of the reason. So, no big deal!
In the next step I'll ask you to start the Task and the Live Trading Session. If you choose not to, keep going with the tutorial as if you had...
